---
title: Peppercorn-Crusted Rib-Eye Steak with Truffle Mac ’n’ Cheese and Heirloom Tomato Salad
description: When mac ’n’ cheese is on the menu, you know you’re in for a treat. But we’re turning that treat into a bona fide feast with the addition of a glorious rib-eye steak seasoned in freshly cracked peppercorns and a bright salad with heirloom tomatoes. Plus, there’s sumptuous, deeply flavored truffle zest mixed right into the pasta, which is practically guaranteed to make this meal dazzle and delight.
